import {v4 as uuidv4} from 'uuid';

export default function articles() {
    return[
        {
            id:uuidv4(),
            name:'artilce1',
            author:'zein',
            subject:'subject1',
            picture:'https://images4.alphacoders.com/936/thumbbig-936378.webp',
            summery:'summery1',
            context:'contet1',
            date: Date(),
            current : `${Date().getDate()}/${Date().getMonth()+1}/${Date().getFullYear()}`,
            likes:0,
            comments:[]
        },
        {
            id:uuidv4(),
            name:'artilce2',
            author:'zein2',
            subject:'subject2',
            picture:'https://images4.alphacoders.com/936/thumbbig-936378.webp',
            summery:'summery2',
            context:'contet2',
            date: new Date(),
            likes:0,
            comments:[]
        },
        {
            id:uuidv4(),
            name:'artilce3',
            author:'zein',
            subject:'subject3',
            picture:'https://images2.alphacoders.com/805/thumbbig-805200.webp',
            summery:'summery3',
            context:'contet3',
            date: new Date(),
            likes:0,
            comments:[]
        }

    ]
};
